\end_inset

where 
\begin_inset Formula $\tau(x)$
\end_inset

 is the triangle wave: 
\begin_inset Formula \[
\tau(x)=\left\{ \begin{array}{ccc}
2x & \;\textrm{ when }\; & 0\leq x\leq1/2\\
2(1-x) & \;\textrm{ when }\; & 1/2\leq x\leq1\end{array}\right.\]

\end_inset


